      "description": "This E46 M3 is a turn-key collector specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including a reinforced rear subframe and updated rod bearings. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, with all bushings and dampers providing the firm, communicative feedback expected of a flagship M-car. This is a mechanically flawless example with a pristine chassis and zero deferred maintenance.",
